OL,3,CFormer MSP to face trial over drink-
OL,4,Cdriving allegations
OL,6,FA former Labour MSP will stand trial
OL,7,Fin November over allegations he caused
OL,8,Fmultiple crashes in central Edinburgh
OL,9,Fwhile over the drink-drive limit.
OL,11,FColin Smyth, 53, is alleged to have
OL,12,Fdriven dangerously on the city's High
OL,13,FStreet and elsewhere on 2 November
OL,14,Flast year, while at more than double
OL,15,Fthe legal alcohol limit.
OL,17,FIt is alleged that after mounting a
OL,18,Fpavement, he narrowly missed a
OL,19,Fpedestrian and collided with a parked
OL,20,Fcar, while driving at excessive speed.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/3
