OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F321A1783521456
OL,3,CFormer MSP to face trial over drink-
OL,4,Cdriving allegations
OL,6,FIt is also alleged he crashed into
OL,7,Felectric bollards directly outside
OL,8,FCity Chambers, and that he repeatedly
OL,9,Fgot in and out of the vehicle and
OL,10,Frevved the engine.
OL,12,FThe former South Scotland MSP is also
OL,13,Faccused of failing to report the
OL,14,Fincident to police "as soon as
OL,15,Freasonably practicable".
OL,17,FHe denies the allegations.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/3
