OL,3,CFormer MSP to face trial over drink-
OL,4,Cdriving allegations
OL,6,FDuring a brief hearing at Edinburgh
OL,7,FSheriff Court on Wednesday, Sheriff
OL,8,FIain Nicol fixed a trial date for 27
OL,9,FNovember.
OL,11,FSmyth, who appeared in court dressed
OL,12,Fin a dark grey suit and red tie, spoke
OL,13,Fonly to confirm his name.
OL,15,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,16,Four political experts are across all
OL,17,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,18,Fto the latest episode below...
